candidates.body:

crate named "spiffe".

**Note:**  the `spiffe` branch will be deleted when this PR is merged.

candidates.title: Add a JWT-SVID authentication method
candidates.body:
Using this method, the client will fetch its JWT-SVID and send it in the
authentication field.
The socket endpoint is found through the SPIFFE_ENDPOINT_SOCKET
environment variable.

candidates.title: Remove filesystem checks
candidates.body:
This commit removes the filesystem checks for correct permissions on
Parsec "assets". The checks can now be removed because the new locations
in the filesystem mean that only a privileged user can create the files.

Fixes #51
